title: Sound On: SWIFT, Ukrainian Resistance, Trump Putin Praise
itunes:title: Sound On: SWIFT, Ukrainian Resistance, Trump Putin Praise
description:
Guests: Stephen Mull, former Ambassador to Poland and Vice Provost for Global Affairs at the University of Virginia, Retired Lieutenant General Ben Hodges, former Commander of US Army Europe and Center for European Policy Analysis Pershing Chair in Strategic Studies, and Bloomberg Politics Contributors Jeanne Sheehan Zaino and Rick Davis.
